36477abde5597fcJmltdHM9MTc3NjIxMTIwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=0bdb237c-209d-67fd-12ea-3440214e66e5&amp;psq=vw+passat&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9lbi53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvVm9sa3N3YWdlbl9QYXNzYXQjQjFfKFR5cGVfMzI7XzE5NzMp&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5465.1"></a><div class="acf_t_c_content "><div class="acf_t_c_inner"><div class="acf_t_c_title_cont"><div style="-webkit-line-clamp: 1; line-clamp: 1;" class="acf_t_c_title" role="heading" aria-level="2">B1 (Type 32; 1973)</div><div class="acf_t_c_chevron_container"><div class="acf_t_c_chevron_icon"><svg id="acfchevronicon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M6.40617 3.20041C6.10264 3.48226 6.08506 3.95681 6.36691 4.26034L9.89303 8L6.36691 11.7397C6.08506 12.0432 6.10264 12.5177 6.40617 12.7996C6.7097 13.0815 7.18425 13.0639 7.4661 12.7603L11.4661 8.51034C11.7333 8.22258 11.7333 7.77743 11.4661 7.48966L7.4661 3.23966C7.18425 2.93613 6.7097 2.91856 6.40617 3.20041Z"></path></svg></div></div></div><p style="-webkit-line-clamp: 6; line-clamp: 6; overflow:hidden;" class="acf_t_c_body">The first generation Passat launched in 1973 in two- and four-door sedan and three- and five-door versions. Externally all four shared styling by Giorgetto Giugiaro. The first generation Passat was a fastback variant of the mechanically identical Audi …</p></div></div></div></div><div class="b_wikiGbModImageCard"><div class="b_bimgSetrcw"><div class="bimgclgsw19113"><div class="cico b_bwrich_icma" style="width:310px;height:198px;"><a title="View details" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/images/search?view=detailV2&amp;q=imgurl:https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9b/VW_Passat_Variant_Elegance_%28B9%29_%E2%80%93_f_18052025.jpg/330px-VW_Passat_Variant_Elegance_%28B9%29_%E2%80%93_f_18052025.jpg&amp;iss=sbi&amp;mode=overlay&amp;idpbck=1&amp;idpp=WikiGoBig&amp;FORM=IDPWGB&amp;thid=ODL.87c33aed35fe237a84b0326827a8b080&amp;mediaurl=https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9b/VW_Passat_Variant_Elegance_%28B9%29_%E2%80%93_f_18052025.jpg/330px-VW_Passat_Variant_Elegance_%28B9%29_%E2%80%93_f_18052025.jpg" h="ID=SERP,5464.1" data-idpignore="1"><img height="198" width="310" data-src-hq="https://th.bing.com/th/id/ODL.87c33aed35fe237a84b0326827a8b080?w=310&amp;h=198&amp;c=7&amp;rs=1&amp;bgcl=ffff14&amp;r=0&amp;o=6&amp;pid=AlgoBlockDebug" role="presentation" data-priority="2" id="emb16A52089" class="rms_img" src="./passat_files/ODL.87c33aed35fe237a84b0326827a8b080" data-bm="24"></a></div></div></div></div><div class="b_wikiGbModImageCard"><div class="b_bimgSetrcw"><div class="bimgclgsw1919"><div class="cico b_bwrich_icma" style="width:206px;height:198px;"><a title="View details" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/images/search?view=detailV2&amp;q=imgurl:https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Passat_b2_bag.jpg/250px-Passat_b2_bag.jpg&amp;iss=sbi&amp;mode=overlay&amp;idpbck=1&amp;idpp=WikiGoBig&amp;FORM=IDPWGB&amp;thid=ODL.a1c33bff6ef2f98983fd1dd0f94b9a1c&amp;mediaurl=https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Passat_b2_bag.jpg/250px-Passat_b2_bag.jpg" h="ID=SERP,5467.1" data-idpignore="1"><img height="198" width="206" data-src-hq="https://th.bing.com/th/id/ODL.a1c33bff6ef2f98983fd1dd0f94b9a1c?w=206&amp;h=198&amp;c=7&amp;rs=1&amp;bgcl=fffffc&amp;r=0&amp;o=6&amp;pid=AlgoBlockDebug" role="presentation" data-priority="2" id="emb14D5AE866" class="rms_img" src="./passat_files/ODL.a1c33bff6ef2f98983fd1dd0f94b9a1c" data-bm="25"></a></div></div><div class="bimgclgsw15913"><div class="cico b_bwrich_icma" style="width:102px;height:98px;"><a title="View details" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/images/search?view=detailV2&amp;q=imgurl:https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/77/Volkswagen_Passat_sedan_B3.jpg/250px-Volkswagen_Passat_sedan_B3.jpg&amp;iss=sbi&amp;mode=overlay&amp;idpbck=1&amp;idpp=WikiGoBig&amp;FORM=IDPWGB&amp;thid=ODL.6a26d0cc580e8af3fae4013cd224bd71&amp;mediaurl=https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/77/Volkswagen_Passat_sedan_B3.jpg/250px-Volkswagen_Passat_sedan_B3.jpg" h="ID=SERP,5469.1" data-idpignore="1"><img height="98" width="102" data-src-hq="https://th.bing.com/th/id/ODL.6a26d0cc580e8af3fae4013cd224bd71?w=102&amp;h=98&amp;c=7&amp;rs=1&amp;bgcl=fffffb&amp;r=0&amp;o=6&amp;pid=AlgoBlockDebug" role="presentation" data-priority="2" id="emb2365F3F2B" class="rms_img" src="./passat_files/ODL.6a26d0cc580e8af3fae4013cd224bd71" data-bm="26"></a></div></div><div class="bimgclgsw59913"><div class="cico b_bwrich_icma" style="width:102px;height:98px;"><a title="View details" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/images/search?view=detailV2&amp;q=imgurl:https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/99/1999_Volkswagen_Passat_%283B_MY00%29_V6_Syncro_sedan_%282015-11-11%29_01.jpg/250px-1999_Volkswagen_Passat_%283B_MY00%29_V6_Syncro_sedan_%282015-11-11%29_01.jpg&amp;iss=sbi&amp;mode=overlay&amp;idpbck=1&amp;idpp=WikiGoBig&amp;FORM=IDPWGB&amp;thid=ODL.fd81d752f62975a5b819c07aea5f66a4&amp;mediaurl=https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/99/1999_Volkswagen_Passat_%283B_MY00%29_V6_Syncro_sedan_%282015-11-11%29_01.jpg/250px-1999_Volkswagen_Passat_%283B_MY00%29_V6_Syncro_sedan_%282015-11-11%29_01.jpg" h="ID=SERP,5471.1" data-idpignore="1"><img height="98" width="102" data-src-hq="https://th.bing.com/th/id/ODL.fd81d752f62975a5b819c07aea5f66a4?w=102&amp;h=98&amp;c=7&amp;rs=1&amp;bgcl=fffffa&amp;r=0&amp;o=6&amp;pid=AlgoBlockDebug" role="presentation" data-priority="2" id="emb31AC6A3FB" class="rms_img" src="./passat_files/ODL.fd81d752f62975a5b819c07aea5f66a4" data-bm="27"></a></div></div></div></div><div><div id="b_acf_tc_2806D67" class="b_acf_card b_wikiGbModCard acf_t_c acf_padding b_acf_bckgnd" link=""><a title="" class="b_acf_card_link" target="_blank" tabindex="0" aria-label="B2 (Type 32B; 1981)" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=61e13455de569bb3af8f3ddd24386060432ec53ca88a5e15fb595f09f0f8dc3cJmltdHM9MTc3NjIxMTIwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=0bdb237c-209d-67fd-12ea-3440214e66e5&amp;psq=vw+passat&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9lbi53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvVm9sa3N3YWdlbl9QYXNzYXQjQjJfKFR5cGVfMzJCO18xOTgxKQ&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5466.1"></a><div class="acf_t_c_content "><div class="acf_t_c_inner"><div class="acf_t_c_title_cont"><div style="-webkit-line-clamp: 1; line-clamp: 1;" class="acf_t_c_title" role="heading" aria-level="2">B2 (Type 32B; 1981)</div><div class="acf_t_c_chevron_container"><div class="acf_t_c_chevron_icon"><svg tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#acfchevronicon"></use></svg></div></div></div><p style="-webkit-line-clamp: 6; line-clamp: 6; overflow:hidden;" class="acf_t_c_body">The second generation Passat launched in November 1980. The platform, named B2, was once again based on the corresponding version of the Audi 80, which had been launched in 1978. The B2 Passat was slightly longer. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div elementtiming="frp.MiddleOfPage" aria-hidden="true" style="pointer-events:none;margin-top:-1px;height:1px;width:1px;font-size:1px;position:absolute;top:0;right:0;" tabindex="-1"> &nbsp; </div><div class="b_wiki_license"><div class="wiki_attr b_divdef"><span title="Wikipedia text under CC-BY-SA licence">Wikipedia text under <a target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=72c067600da33badd34b49536031e6ee17a150ae5f9e77353b71e4e0dccc25e4JmltdHM9MTc3NjIxMTIwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=0bdb237c-209d-67fd-12ea-3440214e66e5&amp;psq=vw+passat&amp;u=a1aHR0cDovL2NyZWF0aXZlY29tbW9ucy5vcmcvbGljZW5zZXMvYnktc2EvMy4wLw&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,6011.1">CC-BY-SA licence</a></span></div></div><div class="b_gobig_feedback"><div id="fdbk_thmb3" class="fdbk_thmb_root  " data-priority="2" aria-live="polite"><div id="fdbk_emotion3" class="fdbk_emotion"><img src="./passat_files/th" class="sat_img"><img src="./passat_files/th(1)" class="dsat_img"></div><span id="fdbtext_3" class="fd